data.description:
Price reduced!!  Very nice home is a sought after area in SW Norman.  New interior and exterior paint and carpeting along with remodeled bathrooms.  There is wet bar between the kitchen and living room which makes this home great for entertaining.
Newer windows and many more updates.  This home is on a large corner lot and has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with a formal dining room.   The living room is large and features a fireplace and bookshelves on each side.
In excellent shape and not far from the OU campus and not far from HW9 and I35.
Listing broker is an owner of the selling company with license #071687.
Seller will consider owner financing with 20% down at 6.5% up to 30 years subject to credit/income review.
